Package com.impinj.octanesdk Description

This package contains the classes and methods to access Impinj readers through Java

Key classes in the Octane SDK Java

  • ImpinjReader: This class controls connection to the reader and the querying and applying of reader settings

  • Settings: this class provides a container for all the reader settings

  • Features: This class provides all of the feature information to the application can know what features are available on each reader
